{"id":"810700606099570688","type":"photo","timestamp":1773144346,"post_url":"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/goodtransgirl/810700606099570688","is_reblog":true,"added_content":true,"tags":[],"reblog_ready":true,"caption":"<p><a href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/transgarnets/810700503964139520/goodtransgirl-youwantedfrightening\" class=\"tumblr_blog\">transgarnets</a>:</p>\n\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/goodtransgirl/810698451521323008/youwantedfrightening-blukirbita\" class=\"tumblr_blog\">goodtransgirl</a>:</p>\n\n<blockquote><p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"http://youwantedfrightening.tumblr.com/post/64199250668/blukirbita-livid-righteousness-badgers-a\">youwantedfrightening</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"http://blukirbita.tumblr.com/post/43365395603/livid-righteousness-badgers-a-metaphor-for\">blukirbita</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"http://livid-righteousness-badgers.tumblr.com/post/36328974154/a-metaphor-for-being-forced-to-choose-a-life-path\">livid-righteousness-badgers</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>a metaphor for being forced to choose a life path when you’re 18</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>or you could just become a magical girl</p>\n<p><img alt=\"image\" height=\"297\" src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/751ac7a35ee6ef376afcf582b0db5def/tumblr_mi84vy8w761s2kalqo2_500.gif\" width=\"500\"/></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>this post speaks to me on a spiritual level</p>\n</blockquote>\n\n\n<p>I waited a little longer than 18 to choose the magical girl path, but I love it, but I got here!</p></blockquote>\n\n\n<p>Sameeee though the signs were there and I should’ve realized earlier… but we’re here now!</p></blockquote>\n\n\n<p>I knew much earlier, but growing up in the South in the 80s and 90s, it took me a long time to be willing to open that closet door.</p>","trail":[{"blog":{"name":"livid-righteousness-badgers","active":true,"theme":{"avatar_shape":"square","background_color":"#FAFAFA","body_font":"Hel